How to protect your skin & hair after you play Holi!
1. Do not use alcoholic tone, lemon or scrub to take out your color, completely no no❌
✅ Use a cleansing milk to remove off the colour

2. Take a bath with only lukewarm water - avoid very hot water 

3. Use a gentle shampoo, conditioner & hair serum 

4. Moisturiser your face & body

5. Do not forget to hydrate your body keep having plenty of water!
